{"tid":1131965,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"杜汶澤卸膊話自己俾兄弟跣鳩咗","createTime":"2019-04-30T03:51:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T04:51:30.000Z","uid":19386,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a003e705706931ee1c7befa223d3bc0bb44982b7","tid":1131965,"uid":19386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T03:51:36.000Z","msg":"兄弟：<br />\n<br />\n由破事兒識你，你由做𡃁仔跟住楊仔，一路到你自立門戶，幫我監製嘅戲做製片，到我做導演，你做執行監製，你做嘢都好交帶！<br />\n<br />\n我仲記得當日我要開網台，點鳩你叫你幫我做一個月，搞下呢樣搞下嗰樣，結果一搞就搞咗年鳩幾，你為咗幫我，仲要放棄埋自己最想做嘅電影。<br />\n我心入面一直好感激你！<br />\n<br />\n無錯，雖然呢鑊嘢比你跣鳩咗，但係做兄弟嘅嘢，無話邊個跣邊個，你做啱一萬樣嘢，唔通你做錯一樣我就怪你？無可能！<br />\n<br />\n以後繼續比心機，做好啲啲嘢，出嚟行同人嘈唔一定鑊鑊打贏嘅，捱一兩刀，唔死得人嘅！<br />\n<br />\n怪就怪我無請多個人幫輕你。<br />\n<br />\n總之大家心撚照，唔好擺響心，吓！<br />\n<br />\n點解我要出公開信？因為驚你又已讀不回囉⋯⋯<br />\n聽晚見啦！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100003717698520/posts/1532196740247568?s=1312826125&amp;v=i&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100003717698520%2Fposts%2F1532196740247568%3Fs%3D1312826125%26v%3Di%26sfns%3Dmo&d=exB9%2BbP5di4RF4u3Oz7pYhA11HdiY488GD%2FHa51CVEA%3D&h=fa0870d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100003717698520/posts/1532196740247568?s=1312826125&amp;v=i&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f71a92a362fec183d8dd90b323c8b72dd9e185aa","tid":1131965,"uid":2757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T04:03:36.000Z","msg":"依家真係呀豬呀狗都可以出嚟做老細嗰喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"690ee1387b33a166096f6f96af04fba5996d972d","tid":1131965,"uid":44698,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T04:04:46.000Z","